            <title>[PDFBOX-4480] Problem extracting text in newline characters and spaces beetween words</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-4480</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have a PDF file , when I try to extract its text using&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It ignores some Enter characters between lines, so the last word in the line and the first word in the next line appear as 1 word without spaces between them !!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For Example, In Attached Pdf&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;main Bsk as mainBsk&lt;/p&gt;

